Summary: Orange fireball moved from west to east north of Trophy Club, Tx
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile sitting at the dining room table we saw a bright fireball moving across the sky and we immediately went outside to see. The fireball moved from west to east much like an airplane, but definatly wasn't. The object appeared to be bright orange and on fire.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Trophy Club
